title: DiCUNO B22 to E14 Socket Converter, Bayonet to Small Screw Adapter, BC to SES Converter, 0-250V, 165℃ Heat Resistant, 2 Packs
features: Basic information: B22 to E14 Converter/Bayonet to Small Screw. The max wattage is 100W, voltage is 0-250V. 165℃ heat resistant.

Easy to install: No need tools to install, simply screw the socket adapt into B22/Bayonet type socket, then screw in E14/Small Screw bulb. Please keep it out of a small confined space for heat dissipation.

Application: Ideal for LED, halogen, filament or CFL light bulb. This Socket Converter allows you to choose more LED lights to adapt to your fixture or base, rather than replace you fixtures with a new one.
Reliable After-sales: 3-month refund and 1-year warranty. If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us.
Tips: Please do not screw or push it too hard! Any problem please contact DiCUNO first, we will provide solutions.
description: Product Description DiCUNO is a professional provider specializing in home and commercial lighting.
